title: Denis Fomin
text:
Denis Aleksandrovich Fomin (; born 3 May 1996) is a Russian <a href="association%20football">football</a> <a href="Defender%20%28association%20football%29">defender</a>. He plays for <a href="FC%20SKA-Khabarovsk">FC SKA-Khabarovsk</a>.
Club career.
He made his debut in the <a href="Russian%20Second%20Division">Russian Second Division</a> for <a href="FC%20Tekstilshchik%20Ivanovo">FC Tekstilshchik Ivanovo</a> on 20 April 2013 in a game against <a href="FC%20Znamya%20Truda%20Orekhovo-Zuyevo">FC Znamya Truda Orekhovo-Zuyevo</a>.
He made his <a href="Russian%20Premier%20League">Russian Premier League</a> debut on 7 March 2015 for <a href="FC%20Ural%20Yekaterinburg">FC Ural Yekaterinburg</a> in a game against <a href="FC%20Zenit%20Saint%20Petersburg">FC Zenit Saint Petersburg</a>.
